    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-创建github仓库"><a href="#1-创建github仓库" class="headerlink" title="1.创建github仓库"></a>1.创建github仓库</h2><p>在创建github仓库的时候，有一些讲究；仓库的名称必须是<code>&lt;username&gt;</code> + <code>github.com</code>组合<br>例如我的就是： <code>Junglezt.github.com</code></p><p><img src="/../img/image.png" alt="alt text"></p><h2 id="2-在本地搭建hexo"><a href="#2-在本地搭建hexo" class="headerlink" title="2.在本地搭建hexo"></a>2.在本地搭建hexo</h2><blockquote><p>hexo是一个轻量级，专门为个人建立网站的博客框架</p></blockquote><h2 id="2-1-安装-hexo"><a href="#2-1-安装-hexo" class="headerlink" title="2.1 安装 hexo"></a>2.1 安装 hexo</h2><p><code>hexo</code>依赖<code>node</code>环境，首先我们需要安装<code>node</code><br>参考<code>node</code>官网: <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download</a></p><p>下载后使用<code>npm</code>安装<code>hexo</code>网站<br>参考<code>hexo</code>官网: <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install hexo-cli -g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../img/image-1.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>hexo有一些常用的命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo init &lt;name&gt;    # 构建一个 hexo 网站<br>hexo server         # 在本地启动 4000 端口的 hexo 网站<br>hexo clean          # 清楚缓存文件<br>hexo deploy         # 将文件部署到 &lt;username&gt;.github.io 中<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-2-构建并部署-hexo"><a href="#2-2-构建并部署-hexo" class="headerlink" title="2.2 构建并部署 hexo"></a>2.2 构建并部署 hexo</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo init helloHexo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../img/image-2.png" alt="alt text"></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd helloHexo<br>npm install     # 让 npm 监测并安装依赖<br>hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../img/image-4.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>访问即可看到默认的hexo网站: <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a><br><img src="/../img/image-3.png" alt="alt text"></p><h2 id="2-3-安装hexo主题及插件"><a href="#2-3-安装hexo主题及插件" class="headerlink" title="2.3 安装hexo主题及插件"></a>2.3 安装hexo主题及插件</h2><blockquote><p>hexo的主题一般在 themes目录中，hexo官方提供了很多的主题</p></blockquote><p>主题网址: <a href="https://hexo.io/themes/">https://hexo.io/themes/</a></p><p>这里我使用hexploit主题，首先使用<code>git</code>下载主题<br>作者Bilibili: <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV18qQkYuEaD/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV18qQkYuEaD/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click</a><br>github: <a href="https://github.com/m310ct/hexo-theme-hexploit?tab=readme-ov-file">https://github.com/m310ct/hexo-theme-hexploit?tab=readme-ov-file</a><br>参考网址: <a href="https://m310ct.com/2025/01/24/hexploit%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/">https://m310ct.com/2025/01/24/hexploit%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</a></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd themes<br>git clone https://github.com/m310ct/hexo-theme-hexploit.git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着修改项目根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，修改主题</p><blockquote><p>注： 这里的主题名称是 themes 目录下，主题文件夹的名称</p></blockquote><p><img src="/../img/image-5.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>该主题需要一些插件<br><strong>1.RSS插件</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">在hexo网站根目录</span><br>npm install hexo-generator-feed --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">feed:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">rss</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">path:</span> <span class="hljs-string">rss.xml</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2.搜索插件</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">在hexo网站根目录</span><br>npm install hexo-generator-search --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">search:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">path:</span> <span class="hljs-string">search.json</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">field:</span> <span class="hljs-string">all</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">format:</span> <span class="hljs-string">html</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">limit:</span> <span class="hljs-number">10000</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>3.添加对应页面</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo new page categories<br><br>hexo new page tags<br><br>hexo new page about<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>4.修改主题配置文件</strong><br><code>/themes/hexplhexo-theme-hexploitoit/_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">menu:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Home</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Archives</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/archives</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Categories</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/categories</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Tags</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/tags</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">About</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/about</span><br>  <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">RSS</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">/rss.xml</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">sidebar:</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#侧边栏</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span> <br>  <span class="hljs-attr">widgets:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">search</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#搜索</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">notice</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#公告</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">categories</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#分类</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">tags</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#标签</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-string">links</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#链接</span><br><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">numlimit:</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 限制侧边栏显示的数量</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">categories:</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">tags:</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span><br>    <br>  <span class="hljs-attr">links:</span><br>    <span class="hljs-bullet">-</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name:</span> <span class="hljs-string">百度</span><br>      <span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://www.baidu.com</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">notice:</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 公告栏内容</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 设置为 true 启用，false 禁用</span><br>    <span class="hljs-attr">content:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;博客正在进行优化，敬请期待更多内容！&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 公告栏显示的内容</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>5.代码高亮</strong><br>修改<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">highlight:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">line_number:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">auto_detect:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">tab_replace:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">wrap:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">hljs:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">prismjs:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">enable:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">preprocess:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">line_number:</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">tab_replace:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置完毕可以停止<code>hexo</code>，再次启动，查看主题是否生效</p><h2 id="3-配置hexo本地更新github-io托管"><a href="#3-配置hexo本地更新github-io托管" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置hexo本地更新github.io托管"></a>3. 配置hexo本地更新github.io托管</h2><p>参考官网: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/github-pages">https://hexo.io/docs/github-pages</a></p><p>安装<code>hexo-deployer-git</code>插件</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改<code>_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repository:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git@github.com:Junglezt/Junglezt.github.io.git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">main</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>官网默认的配置是使用<code>token</code>的方式验证，我没有认证成功，上述可以看出我使用的是<code>ssh</code>连接，步骤如下</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;&lt;you-emial&gt;&quot;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行后一直回车，默认会在用户的家目录中创建一个<code>.ssh</code>的目录，其中有<code>id_rsa、id_rsa.pub</code>文件<br>Windows: <code>c:\users\&lt;username&gt;\.ssh\</code><br>Linux: <code>/home/&lt;username&gt;/.ssh</code><br><img src="/../img/image-6.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>接着登录到github后台，<code>头像 -&gt; Setting -&gt; SSH and GPG keys -&gt; New SSH key</code><br><code>title</code>起一个容易记忆名字: Junglezt.github.io<br>复制<code>id_rsa.pub</code>文件中的所有内容到<code>Key</code>，点击<code>ADD SSH Key</code><br><img src="/../img/image-7.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>如果添加成功，可以使用<code>ssh</code>命令测试是否添加成功</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">ssh -T git@github.com<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/../img/image-8.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>如果上述配置成功，执行<code>hexo d</code>即可同步到<code>github.io</code>个人网站</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
